AVAILABILITY DATE: December

Why Rent with us?

Lease with the peace of mind of locked-in rent amounts and purchase prices. Live in the Home as a renter with the option to buy it anytime. At the end of your 1-year lease term, you can renew for another year or walk away with no penalties.

Property Description:
BOND PAID. 3 bedroom 2 Bath Amarillo TURN-KEY in coveted Village of Summerhill in The Villages. As of Sept 2022, installed ALL NEW stainless steel appliances and hardware in the kitchen comprised of 'All Around Cooling' refrigerator, GAS stove/oven with griddle, convection, air fryer, trendy single bowl sink, and microwave. NEW washer & NEW GAS dryer. GAS heating and GAS water heater in this Open Floor Plan. NEW modern LED fixtures including ALL can bath lighting, chandelier, sconces, and ceiling fans. NEW NEST Learning Thermostat, RING doorbell added to security system and a garage fridge. Driveway, garage, enclosed lanai ALL custom painted. New Seller Home Inspection - repairs completed - Report available. Minutes by golf cart to vast amenities that being a Villager offers. Short Golf Cart ride to Sumter Landing & Spanish Springs. Near ALL important on 466. HOME WARRANTY offered by SELLER. 

GARAGE/PARKING: 2 Attached garage 

KITCHEN/LAUNDRY APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Dishwasher, Disposal, Dryer, Gas Water Heater, Microwave, Range, Refrigerator, Washer, Water Filtration System.

Pet Restrictions: We allow up to 3 pets (cats or dogs) weighing less than 180 pounds in total combined weight. We allow all dog breeds; however, certain dog breeds may be restricted by local regulations and Homeowner's Association rules. 

Pet Deposit: One-time nonrefundable $300 fee per pet and $30 monthly rent for up to three pets.
